#: ../../doc/utility.rst:144
msgid "Atomic Reference Counting"
msgstr "原子引用计数"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:146
msgid ""
"``atomic_counter`` wraps AngelScript's ``asAtomicInc`` / ``asAtomicDec`` for "
"thread-safe reference counting. It is designed for implementing the "
"``addref`` / ``release`` / ``get_refcount`` behaviours of a garbage-"
"collected ``ref_class``."
msgstr ""
"``atomic_counter`` 包装 AngelScript 的 ``asAtomicInc`` / ``asAtomicDec``，用于"
"线程安全的引用计数。它专为实现垃圾回收的 ``ref_class`` 的 ``addref`` / "
"``release`` / ``get_refcount`` 行为而设计。"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:150
msgid ""
"Constructing an ``atomic_counter`` initializes the counter to 1. Prefix ``+"
"+`` and ``--`` call ``asAtomicInc`` and ``asAtomicDec`` respectively, "
"returning the new value. The ``dec_and_try_destroy`` method decrements and, "
"if the counter reaches 0, invokes a destroyer callback — typically "
"``delete`` on the enclosing object."
msgstr ""
"构造 ``atomic_counter`` 会将计数器初始化为 1。前缀 ``++`` 和 ``--`` 分别调用 "
"``asAtomicInc`` 和 ``asAtomicDec``，返回新值。``dec_and_try_destroy`` 方法递减"
"计数器，如果计数器达到 0，则调用销毁回调——通常是对封闭对象执行 ``delete``。"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:154
msgid ""
"Example: implementing reference counting for a garbage-collected script "
"object:"
msgstr "示例：为垃圾回收的脚本对象实现引用计数："

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:205
msgid ""
"See :ref:`the threading documentation <atomic-refcounting>` for the full API "
"reference."
msgstr ""
"完整 API 参考请参见 :ref:`线程文档 <atomic-refcounting>`。"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:208
msgid "Range Views"
msgstr "范围视图"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:210
msgid ""
"asbind20 provides range views for iterating over AngelScript entities — type "
"members, behaviours, enum values, and even tokenized script source. When "
"``<ranges>`` is available (``__cpp_lib_ranges``), these views integrate with "
"standard range adaptors and algorithms."
msgstr ""
"asbind20 提供了用于遍历 AngelScript 实体的范围视图——类型成员、行为、枚举值，甚"
"至是分词后的脚本源代码。当 ``<ranges>`` 可用时（``__cpp_lib_ranges``），这些视图"
"可以与标准范围适配器和算法集成。"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:214
msgid ""
"All views expose ``begin()``/``end()``, ``size()``, and ``empty()``. Most "
"iterators are random-access."
msgstr ""
"所有视图都公开 ``begin()``/``end()``、``size()`` 和 ``empty()``。大多数迭代器是"
"随机访问的。"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:217
msgid "Type information views"
msgstr "类型信息视图"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:219
msgid "These views wrap an ``asITypeInfo*`` and enumerate its contents:"
msgstr "这些视图包装 ``asITypeInfo*`` 并枚举其内容："

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:247
msgid ""
"The ``all_enum_values`` factory defaults to ``int`` as the underlying type. "
"Use ``views::all_enum_values_of<std::uint64_t>(ti)`` for enums with a custom "
"underlying type."
msgstr ""
"``all_enum_values`` 工厂默认使用 ``int`` 作为底层类型。对于具有自定义底层类型的"
"枚举，使用 ``views::all_enum_values_of<std::uint64_t>(ti)``。"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:267
msgid "Tokenize view"
msgstr "分词视图"

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:269
msgid ""
"``tokenize_view`` tokenizes a string of AngelScript source code lazily, "
"yielding ``(asETokenClass, std::string_view)`` pairs:"
msgstr ""
"``tokenize_view`` 延迟地对 AngelScript 源代码字符串进行分词，生成 "
"``(asETokenClass, std::string_view)`` 对："

#: ../../doc/utility.rst:282
msgid ""
"The view is an input range — it does not support random access or multi-pass "
"iteration."
msgstr "该视图是输入范围——它不支持随机访问或多遍迭代。"

